<div class="D(tbc)" data-reactid="5">Hemp, Inc.&#194;&#160;(OTC PINK: HEMP), a global leader in the industrial hemp industry with the largest hemp mill in the western hemisphere, announced today that the Company applauds the Alaska House of Representatives for unanimously passing&#194;&#160;Senate Bill 6&#194;&#160;Monday, legalizing industrial hemp and establishing a pilot program for its growth and production. The bill was passed with a vote of 36-0.</div>
