<p class="canvas-atom canvas-text Mb(1.0em) Mb(0)--sm Mt(0.8em)--sm" data-reactid="12">SB-6 is &#226;&#128;&#156;an Act relating to the regulation and production of industrial hemp; relating to industrial hemp pilot programs; providing that industrial hemp is not included in the definition of &#8216;marijuana''; providing that cannabidiol oil is not included in the definition of &#8216;hashish oil''; clarifying that adding industrial hemp to food does not create an adulterated food product; and providing for an effective date,&#226;&#128;&#157; according to Alaska State Legislation&#226;&#128;&#153;s website.</p>
<p class="canvas-atom canvas-text Mb(1.0em) Mb(0)--sm Mt(0.8em)--sm" style="margin: 0px 0px 1em;" data-reactid="13">Hemp, Inc. and wholly-owned subsidiary Industrial Hemp Manufacturing, LLC have been on the frontlines of advocating for and assisting with legislation that supports the hemp industry nationwide, including in Alaska. Industrial Hemp Manufacturing Regional Sales Manager Jack Bennett recently&#194;&#160;spoke with&#194;&#160;CBS-affiliated KTVA regarding the industry&#226;&#128;&#153;s support for SB.</p>
<p class="canvas-atom canvas-text Mb(1.0em) Mb(0)--sm Mt(0.8em)--sm" data-reactid="14">&#226;&#128;&#156;Our team has been instrumental in advocating for legislation that will allow hemp farming, manufacturing, and production to flourish nationwide,&#226;&#128;&#157; said David Schmitt, COO, Industrial Hemp Manufacturing, LLC. &#226;&#128;&#156;We dedicate countless hours to working with lawmakers and policy influencers to educate them about the benefits of hemp for the U.S. economy as well as provide valuable input on the drafting of legislation to ensure the long-term success of these programs.&#226;&#128;&#157;</p>
<p class="canvas-atom canvas-text Mb(1.0em) Mb(0)--sm Mt(0.8em)--sm" data-reactid="15">Next, SB-6 will go to the Senate for a vote.</p>
<p class="canvas-atom canvas-text Mb(1.0em) Mb(0)--sm Mt(0.8em)--sm" style="margin: 0px 0px 1em;" data-reactid="16">To view the KTVA news clip, click&#194;&#160;here.</p>
