<div class="D(tbc)" data-reactid="5">Cannabis Science, Inc. (CBIS), a U.S. company specializing in the development of cannabinoid-based medicines, is very pleased to report the Company&#226;&#128;&#153;s groundbreaking laboratory research with Dana-Farber Cancer Institute using Nanoparticle Drone technology and Cannabinoids to successfully kill cancer cells has now reached a serious level of attention. The Cannabis Science Dana-Farber research team has now begun next level planning to bring this efficacious research to full commercialization.</div>
