<p class="canvas-atom canvas-text Mb(1.0em) Mb(0)--sm Mt(0.8em)--sm" style="margin: 0px 0px 1em;" data-reactid="16">Previously, Hemp, Inc.&#194;&#160;announced&#194;&#160;its support of the Alaska House of Representatives&#226;&#128;&#153; unanimous passage of a bill to legalize industrial hemp and establish a pilot program.</p>
