							</div>', '2018-03-02 00:00:00', 'https://www.marijuana.com/news/2018/03/georgia-house-votes-to-add-ptsd-to-medical-marijuana-program/', 9, '2018-03-02 18:45:29.487975', '2018-03-06 13:15:50.635625', 21, NULL, NULL, 0, 'georgia-house-votes-to-add-ptsd-to-medical-marijuana-program');
INSERT INTO articles VALUES (12610, '8 Stash Jars for Weed Storage', NULL, '8-stash-jars-weed-storage-header-1280x800.jpg', '<div class="uncode_text_column"><p>Stash jars are an often overlooked (yet essential) accessory for keeping your recently bought cannabis both potent and organized. The typical plastic baggies often used by growers won&#8217;t cut it when it comes to <a href="https://www.leafly.com/news/cannabis-101/how-long-is-my-cannabis-good-for-leaflys-guide-to-storing-cannabi">maintaining freshness</a> as they&#8217;re often porous, leading to <a href="https://www.leafly.com/news/cannabis-101/identifying-cannabis-past-shelf-life">dry-out and damage</a> to the efficacy of your green.<br>
