INSERT INTO articles VALUES (12575, 'The Products that Powered Weedmaps Pipe House 2018', NULL, 'EMERY_WEEDMAPS_2018_HI_RES-2475-copy-2-702x336.jpg', '<div class="post-content description" itemprop="articleBody">
			
				<div class="nc_socialPanel swp_flatFresh swp_d_fullColor swp_i_fullColor swp_o_fullColor scale-100 scale-fullWidth" data-position="both" data-float="floatNone" data-count="4" data-floatcolor="#ffffff" data-emphasize="0"><div class="nc_tweetContainer swp_fb" data-id="2" data-network="facebook"><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marijuana.com%2Fnews%2F2018%2F02%2Fthe-products-that-powered-weedmaps-pipe-house-2018%2F" data-link="http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marijuana.com%2Fnews%2F2018%2F02%2Fthe-products-that-powered-weedmaps-pipe-house-2018%2F" class="nc_tweet"><span class="swp_count swp_hide"><span class="iconFiller"><span class="spaceManWilly"><i class="sw sw-facebook"></i><span class="swp_share"> Share</span></span></span></span></a></div><div class="nc_tweetContainer twitter" data-id="1" data-network="twitter"><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/share?original_referer=/&amp;text=The+Products+that+Powered+Weedmaps+Pipe+House+2018&amp;url=https://www.marijuana.com/news/2018/02/the-products-that-powered-weedmaps-pipe-house-2018/" data-link="https://twitter.com/share?original_referer=/&amp;text=The+Products+that+Powered+Weedmaps+Pipe+House+2018&amp;url=https://www.marijuana.com/news/2018/02/the-products-that-powered-weedmaps-pipe-house-2018/" class="nc_tweet"><span class="swp_count swp_hide"><span class="iconFiller"><span class="spaceManWilly"><i class="sw sw-twitter"></i><span class="swp_share"> Tweet</span></span></span></span></a></div><div class="nc_tweetContainer linkedIn" data-id="3" data-network="linked_in"><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marijuana.com%2Fnews%2F2018%2F02%2Fthe-products-that-powered-weedmaps-pipe-house-2018%2F" data-link="https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marijuana.com%2Fnews%2F2018%2F02%2Fthe-products-that-powered-weedmaps-pipe-house-2018%2F" class="nc_tweet"><span class="swp_count swp_hide"><span class="iconFiller"><span class="spaceManWilly"><i class="sw sw-linkedin"></i><span class="swp_share"> Share</span></span></span></span></a></div><div class="nc_tweetContainer nc_pinterest" data-id="4" data-network="pinterest"><a rel="nofollow" onclick="var e=document.createElement(''script'');e.setAttribute(''type'',''text/javascript'');e.setAttribute(''charset'',''UTF-8'');e.setAttribute(''src'',''//assets.pinterest.com/js/pinmarklet.js?r=''+Math.random()*99999999);document.body.appendChild(e);" class="nc_tweet noPop"><span class="swp_count swp_hide"><span class="iconFiller"><span class="spaceManWilly"><i class="sw sw-pinterest"></i><span class="swp_share"> Pin</span></span></span></span></a></div></div><p><span style="font-weight: 400">For the second annual pilgrimage to Pipe House for the Weedmaps action sports team, the focus was on relaxation &#8212; a chance to bask in Hawaiian paradise while catching some rays and waves. Not to let legal speak take you away from imagining your happy place, but we should mention that Marijuana.com is owned by Weedmaps.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Over the course of their trip, athletes from the Weedmaps surf, skate, and motocross teams converged on the cannabis-centric compound to reconnect with friends, compete in the DaHui Backdoor Shootout and try cannabis products to aid in their recovery.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Whether the athletes needed CBD to recover from a fresh injury or some Indica flower to wind down at the end of the night in preparation for early morning swells, there was something for everyone this year at WM Pipe House.</span></p>
<div id="attachment_76348" style="max-width: 1010px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="wp-image-76348 size-full" src="https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6A6A4837-copy.jpg" alt="brand-weedmaps-pipe-house" width="1000" height="667" srcset="https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6A6A4837-copy.jpg 1000w, https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6A6A4837-copy-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6A6A4837-copy-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6A6A4837-copy-300x200@2x.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px"><p class="wp-caption-text"><em>Photo: Billy Kember, who used the CBD Drip from <a href="https://weedmaps.com/brands/cbd-drip" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Eco Sciences</a> faithfully during his stay at Pipe House</em></p></div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Here are some of the athlete&#8217;s most loved products (in no particular order), including some honest testimonials from some who needed the products most throughout the trip.</span></p>
<hr>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Hawaii has maintained a certain purity in isolation from the rest of the world, and smokers of Indica impresarios </span><a href="https://weedmaps.com/brands/west-coast-cure/flower" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="font-weight: 400">West Coast Cure&#8217;s</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400"> namesake strain WCC OG enjoy the same level of immaculacy thanks to nitrogen-sealed packaging that keeps your flowers fresh until the very moment you&#8217;re ready to enjoy them.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">WM skate team rider Boo Johnson experienced firsthand how effective&#160;WCC OG really was at diminishing pain and muscle tension in the body, using the cultivar as a comprehensive health plan for the duration of his stay at Pipe House.</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-76350" src="https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6A6A4037-copy.jpg" alt="pipe-house-weedmaps-west-coast-cure-wcc" width="1000" height="667" srcset="https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6A6A4037-copy.jpg 1000w, https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6A6A4037-copy-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6A6A4037-copy-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6A6A4037-copy-300x200@2x.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px"></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">&#8220;The vibe was lavish,&#8221; Boo told Marijuana.com. &#8220;The first joint in the morning had me viewing the beaches through a whole new viewpoint, it was rad. I&#8217;m a huge OG fan and West Coast Cure&#8217;s are A1, they brought a whole new aspect to my trip.&#8221;</span></p>
<hr>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The pungent citrus notes of </span><a href="https://weedmaps.com/brands/paris-og/flower" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="font-weight: 400">Spacewalker OG</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400"> were perfect for island living, so this Paris OG highlight became a fan favorite in the Pipe House. The cross of OG Kush and Skywalker OG is known for mellow full-body effects that pair with intense cerebral pleasure, making it the essential hammock weed at the end of a long day of shredding.</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-76352" src="https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6A6A2114-copy.jpg" alt="weedmaps-pipe-house" width="1000" height="667" srcset="https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6A6A2114-copy.jpg 1000w, https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6A6A2114-copy-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6A6A2114-copy-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6A6A2114-copy-300x200@2x.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px"></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Athletes like skater Marius Syvanen flocked to Spacewalker OG for its out-of-this-world ability to bring them to euphoric places at warp speed.</span></p>
<hr>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The Weedmaps Pipe House experience wasn&#8217;t all about rest and relaxation, as the entire squad was out stacking clips all day, collecting bumps, bruises, and broken bones along the way. While smoking some flower is a great way to combat the grueling toll on the body these guys take at work every day, CBD can take it to the next level, incorporating additional healing properties into the pain relief.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Flav&#8217;s line of </span><a href="https://weedmaps.com/brands/flav/medical/topicals" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="font-weight: 400">CBD products</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400"> kept the team feeling great at Pipe House this year.</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-76354" src="https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_1437-copy.jpg" alt="weedmaps-skate" width="1000" height="667" srcset="https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_1437-copy.jpg 1000w, https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_1437-copy-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_1437-copy-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_1437-copy-300x200@2x.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px"></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">&#8220;I used the Flav CBD salve and the extra strength roll-on topical a lot, actually,&#8217;&#8221; said pro skater Tommy Sandoval. &#8220;The extra-strength is a lifesaver after a long day with sore muscles. I use the salve as more of an all-day thing or whenever I&#8217;m feeling achy or just trying to warm up on the way to the next spot. I&#8217;ll throw it on my knees a lot just to get loose.&#8221;</span></p>
<hr>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">WM MotoCross rider Twitch brought his friends from </span><a href="https://weedmaps.com/brands/quality-resources/flower/pre-rolls" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="font-weight: 400">Quality Resources</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400"> and their pre-rolled collaboration, Twitch Stixx. The</span><a href="https://weedmaps.com/learn/introduction/how-to-buy-cannabis/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="font-weight: 400"> top-shelf </span></a><span style="font-weight: 400">joints come in a variety of strains, but the Gelato, Cookies, and SFV OG were especially popular in the Pipe House this year.</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-76356" src="https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6A6A3373-copy.jpg" alt="weedmaps-motocross" width="1000" height="667" srcset="https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6A6A3373-copy.jpg 1000w, https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6A6A3373-copy-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6A6A3373-copy-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6A6A3373-copy-300x200@2x.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px"></p>
<hr>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">In a paradise like Hawaii, exotic strains are a must, so </span><a href="https://weedmaps.com/brands/connected-cannabis-co/flower" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="font-weight: 400">Connected Cannabis</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400"> came through in the clutch with some of their Guava flower. The pungent Hybrid put the whole team in a state of pure bliss.</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-76358" src="https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Jaws-at-the-table-2018_wm_hawaii151-Hawaii.jpg" alt="weedmaps-pipe-house" width="1000" height="768" srcset="https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Jaws-at-the-table-2018_wm_hawaii151-Hawaii.jpg 1000w, https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Jaws-at-the-table-2018_wm_hawaii151-Hawaii-300x230.jpg 300w, https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Jaws-at-the-table-2018_wm_hawaii151-Hawaii-768x590.jpg 768w, https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Jaws-at-the-table-2018_wm_hawaii151-Hawaii-300x230@2x.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px"></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">&#8220;The Connected Cannabis products were really freaking good, especially the Guava,&#8221; said WM skater Aaron &#8220;Jaws&#8221; Homoki. &#8220;That strain was great in the mornings trying to get up and go skate, definitely made the trip better all-around.&#8221;</span></p>
<p><iframe width="702" height="395" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/fn6FfMnQIoY?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>
<div class="watch-action"><div class="watch-position align-left"><div class="action-like"><a class="lbg-style3 like-76347 jlk" href="javascript:void(0)" data-task="like" data-post_id="76347" data-nonce="4f24dde989" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/plugins/wti-like-post/images/pixel.gif" title="Like"><span class="lc-76347 lc">0</span></a></div><div class="action-unlike"><a class="unlbg-style3 unlike-76347 jlk" href="javascript:void(0)" data-task="unlike" data-post_id="76347" data-nonce="4f24dde989" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.marijuana.com/wp-content/plugins/wti-like-post/images/pixel.gif" title="Unlike"><span class="unlc-76347 unlc">0</span></a></div> </div> <div class="status-76347 status align-left"></div></div><div class="wti-clear"></div><div class="nc_socialPanel swp_flatFresh swp_d_fullColor swp_i_fullColor swp_o_fullColor scale-100 scale-fullWidth" data-position="both" data-float="floatNone" data-count="4" data-floatcolor="#ffffff" data-emphasize="0"><div class="nc_tweetContainer swp_fb" data-id="2" data-network="facebook"><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marijuana.com%2Fnews%2F2018%2F02%2Fthe-products-that-powered-weedmaps-pipe-house-2018%2F" data-link="http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marijuana.com%2Fnews%2F2018%2F02%2Fthe-products-that-powered-weedmaps-pipe-house-2018%2F" class="nc_tweet"><span class="swp_count swp_hide"><span class="iconFiller"><span class="spaceManWilly"><i class="sw sw-facebook"></i><span class="swp_share"> Share</span></span></span></span></a></div><div class="nc_tweetContainer twitter" data-id="1" data-network="twitter"><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/share?original_referer=/&amp;text=The+Products+that+Powered+Weedmaps+Pipe+House+2018&amp;url=https://www.marijuana.com/news/2018/02/the-products-that-powered-weedmaps-pipe-house-2018/" data-link="https://twitter.com/share?original_referer=/&a