<p>(Disclaimer: if you suffer from secondhand embarrassment, watching this <em>will</em> make your skin crawl.)</p>
<p><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/icn10kpsgKY" width="560" height="315" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p>
