<p><iframe id="doc_10958" class="scribd_iframe_embed" title="New Jersey Cannabis Expungement Bill by Rep. Annette Quijano (D-Elizabeth)" src="https://www.scribd.com/embeds/373136910/content?start_page=1&amp;view_mode=scroll&amp;access_key=key-3BEXGPpdZfZ8JjEavOWM&amp;show_recommendations=true" width="100%" height="600" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" data-auto-height="false" data-aspect-ratio="0.6069986541049798"></iframe></p>
