<p class="Lh(36px) Fz(25px)--sm Fz(32px) Mb(17px)--sm Mb(20px) Mb(30px)--lg Ff($ff-primary) Lts($lspacing-md) Fw($fweight) Fsm($fsmoothing) Fsmw($fsmoothing) Fsmm($fsmoothing) Wow(bw)" data-reactid="3">Tetra Bio-Pharma Inc. (&#8220;<strong>Tetra</strong>&#8221; or the &#8220;<strong>Corporation</strong>&#8220;) (TSX VENTURE:TBP)(TBPMF), announced changes to its Board of Directors (the &#8220;Board&#8221;) today, including the appointment of Aphria Inc.&#8217;s Chief Financial Officer (CFO), Mr. Carl Merton, as Chair of Tetra&#8217;s Audit Committee.</p>
