<p class="canvas-atom canvas-text Mb(1.0em) Mb(0)--sm Mt(0.8em)--sm" style="margin: 0px 0px 1em;" data-reactid="14">This pilot project is one of 15 that received funding in the first round of Ontario&#226;&#128;&#153;s $20-million Health Technology Fund. &#194;&#160;The fund is administered by Ontario Centres of Excellence (OCE) on behalf of the Office of the Chief Health Innovation Strategist (OCHIS), and is a part of the OCHIS mandate to strengthen Ontario&#226;&#128;&#153;s health innovation ecosystem.&#194;&#160; For more information please visit&#194;&#160;http://www.oce-ontario.org/programs/commercialization-programs/health-technologies-fund.</p>
