<p>Legal cannabis has changed a few things in Denver, but for the marijuana media mogul who covers the scene in Colorado, it&#8217;s what hasn&#8217;t changed that&#8217;s most noticeable.</p>
<p>&#8220;One of the most striking things is how normal it is,&#8221; said Cassandra Farrington, in an interview Friday on The Homestretch.</p>
<p>&#8220;You can&#8217;t really tell a difference of pre-[recreational]and post-recreational cannabis,&#8221; she said. &#8220;You drive past a dispensary [and]it&#8217;s like driving past a liquor store.</p>
